From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: pve-arm64-builder extension <builder@example.invalid>
Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] add riscv64 and loongarch64 VM architectures

Extend the VM architecture schema to riscv64 and loongarch64, wire their
QEMU binaries, default virt machines, firmware files, CPU defaults and
virt-machine command line handling.

Both new architectures use QEMU's virt machine family. They do not expose
PVE VM-specific CPU flags, matching the existing aarch64 behaviour.
